# Expense Operating Bad Debts Direct To PL Amount

## identifier
de7700

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of bad debts not provided for that have been written off directly to profit and loss during the relevant period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.BadDebtsDirectToPL.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
